Title: Comparison of MasPar MP-1 and MP-2 Communication Operations  
Author: Lutz Prechelt 
Address: D-7500 Karlsruhe, Germany  
Affiliation: Institut fur Programmstrukturen und Datenorganisation Fakultat fur Informatik Universitat Karlsruhe, Postfach 6980  
