Reference: 3. <institution> Xnet communication was not slower on the MP-2 than on the MP-1 for any of the measurements used in this report, </institution> <note> despite the fact that the technical specifications published by MasPar announced reduced bandwith of the xnet on the MP-2. </note>
Reference: 4. <institution> The constant cost of an xfetch or xsend operation is significantly lower on an MP-2. </institution> <note> This can result in a performance above 150% for small distances. </note>
